# Purrfect Match

Monorepo: `backend/` (Laravel 13 + Filament 5) and `frontend/` (Next.js 16).

- Run backend commands from `backend/`, frontend from `frontend/`
- API base: `http://localhost:8000/api`
- Frontend: `http://localhost:3000`
- Auth: Sanctum SPA cookies — never use Bearer tokens for browser auth
- Admin lives in Filament at `/admin` — do not build admin UI in Next.js

When changing API shape, update both backend controllers/resources AND frontend `src/lib/api/` + `src/types/`.
